comments: She is a lovely woman, very nice person! But she is not a good teacher! she will revise essays and make good and helpful suggestions, but otehr than that she is all over the place, has no structure and pretty much no idea what she is talking about! Also her being 20 minutes late to our finals was not so cool!

Ms. Streets is such a nice teacher and person. She takes the time to thoroughly read and comment on/grade papers. Class is fairly easy; Interesting and intriguing essays to write. Flexible but still a good English teacher.
